node.text: Nunca hemos visto tanto apoyo en Estados Unidos para una Cuba libre, no podemos dejar que la pasión o la frustración nos lleven a hacer cosas que nos cueste ese apoyo.

node.title: Seamos apasionados por Cuba, pero seamos también inteligentes.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Senator Marco Rubio on September 11, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'NEVER 9/11 ANNIVERSARY FORGET RUBIO SSEA'.
Photo by Senator Marco Rubio in Jacksonville, Florida with @marcorubiofla, @reprutherfordfl, and @senatormarcorubio. May be an image of one or more people and people standing.

node.text:
I went to Jacksonville to announce our bill the HELPER Act which will eliminate the down payment and monthly mortgage insurance premium requirement for first responders and teachers 
https://www.firstcoastnews.com/article/news/local/new-bill-help-first-responders-teachers-own-homes/77-69d9668d-aec3-42be-b40f-1624b760844e

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Senator Marco Rubio on August 26, 2021. May be an image of dog and indoor.

node.text:
Winston went to bed early because he heard us say its back to school week

But I didn’t have the heart to tell him he can’t go #nationaldogday
